'''线粒体16S RNA'''是一种存在于[[线粒体核糖体|线粒体核糖体]]（mitoribosome，MR）[[39S核糖体亚基|39S核糖体亚基]]中的[[rRNA|rRNA]]。<ref name="pmid11948216">{{cite journal |author=Noda R, Kim CG, Takenaka O, ''et al.'' |title=Mitochondrial 16S rRNA sequence diversity of hominoids |journal=J. Hered. |volume=92 |issue=6 |pages=490–6 |year=2001 |pmid=11948216 |doi= 10.1093/jhered/92.6.490|url=http://jhered.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=11948216}}</ref><ref name="pmid12533837">{{cite journal |author=Nagy A, Wilhelm M, Kovacs G |title=Mutations of mtDNA in renal cell tumours arising in end-stage renal disease |journal=J. Pathol. |volume=199 |issue=2 |pages=237–42 |pmid=12533837 |doi=10.1002/path.1273|date=February 2003}}</ref>在[[人类|人类]][[细胞|细胞]]的[[线粒体|线粒体]]中，该rRNA由[[MT-RNR2|MT-RNR2]][[基因|基因]]编码。MT-RNR2基因还同时编码了能抑制[[阿尔茨海默症|阿尔茨海默症]]相关[[基因表达|基因表达]]的[[humanin|humanin]]。<ref name="pmid12445508">{{cite journal |author=Maximov V, Martynenko A, Hunsmann G, Tarantul V |title=Mitochondrial 16S rRNA gene encodes a functional peptide, a potential drug for Alzheimer's disease and target for cancer therapy |journal=Med. Hypotheses |volume=59 |issue=6 |pages=670–3 |pmid=12445508 |doi= 10.1016/S0306-9877(02)00223-2|url=|date=December 2002}}</ref><ref name="pmid12009529">{{cite journal |author=Tajima H, Niikura T, Hashimoto Y, ''et al.'' |title=Evidence for in vivo production of Humanin peptide, a neuroprotective factor against Alzheimer's disease-related insults |journal=Neurosci. Lett. |volume=324 |issue=3 |pages=227–31 |pmid=12009529 |doi= 10.1016/S0304-3940(02)00199-4|url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0304394002001994|date=May 2002}}</ref>

